              <td style="padding: 1rem;">8 Min Drive</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem;">Modern gym, restaurant, parking</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem;">Groups and medium-stay visitors</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">Rosewood Residences</td>
              <td style="padding: 1rem;">Serviced Apartments</td>
