              <td style="padding: 1rem;">Families and group travel bookings</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h2 id="luxury-picks" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">4. Top Luxury Picks (5-Star): World-Class Opulence</h2>
      
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Four Seasons Hotel Riyadh</h3>
      <p>
        Occupying the upper floors of the iconic Kingdom Centre skyscraper, the Four Seasons Hotel Riyadh represents the pinnacle of modern luxury in the capital. The hotel features spacious rooms with floor-to-ceiling windows offering panoramic views of the city skyline. Guests enjoy access to a heated outdoor swimming pool, a state-of-the-art spa, tennis courts, and several gourmet dining options, including modern Japanese and traditional Middle Eastern cuisine.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Logistical Advantage:</strong> Located in central Olaya, it is a direct 10-minute drive from King Fahd Stadium. Its position within the Kingdom Centre offers immediate, indoor access to high-end shopping galleries and the famous Sky Bridge.
      </p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">The Ritz-Carlton, Riyadh</h3>
      <p>
        Designed to resemble a royal palace, The Ritz-Carlton, Riyadh is situated within 52 acres of beautifully manicured gardens. The property is famous for its grand marble lobbies, indoor swimming pool with a dome canopy, and extensive fine-dining options. It is widely considered the premier address for VIP delegates, official football representatives, and luxury families seeking maximum privacy.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Logistical Advantage:</strong> While located approximately 15 minutes away from the stadium, its isolated and secure grounds provide a calm sanctuary. The hotel concierge frequently coordinates private transport fleets and VIP escorts directly to stadium drop-off zones on match days.
      </p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Mansard Riyadh, A Radisson Collection Hotel</h3>
      <p>
        Located in the upscale northern corridor of the city, Mansard Riyadh combines classic Parisian architecture with modern Saudi luxury. The hotel features beautiful guest rooms, serviced apartments, and standalone three-bedroom villas. Guests can enjoy exceptional fine-dining at the famous L'Ami Dave restaurant, unwind in a state-of-the-art wellness center, or take a peaceful stroll through the European-style cobblestone plazas surrounding the property.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Logistical Advantage:</strong> Situated approximately 12 minutes from the stadium, its location on the northern bypass makes it highly accessible while avoiding the dense traffic of central Olaya. It is an ideal spot for corporate VIPs, business executives, and luxury food enthusiasts.
      </p>

      <h2 id="mid-range" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">5. Best Mid-Range Options (4-Star): Balance of Comfort &amp; Value</h2>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Hilton Riyadh Olaya</h3>
      <p>
        The Hilton Riyadh Olaya is a modern, sleek business hotel located right on Olaya Street. It features comfortable rooms equipped with work desks, ergonomic chairs, and high-speed fiber-optic Wi-Fi. The hotel offers a business center, an executive lounge, a wellness spa, and a reliable international buffet restaurant.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Logistical Advantage:</strong> Located just a 5-minute drive from the stadium, it is one of the closest premium properties. Crucially, it stands within short walking distance of central metro stations, allowing fans to bypass traffic entirely on match days.
      </p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Courtyard by Marriott Riyadh Olaya</h3>
      <p>
        The Courtyard by Marriott Riyadh Olaya offers clean, modern, and highly functional lodging. Known for its friendly service and practical design, the hotel features comfortable bedding, a rooftop pool with city views, and a fully equipped gymnasium. It represents exceptional value for travelers who want Marriott standards without the premium price of a 5-star hotel.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Logistical Advantage:</strong> At an 8-minute drive from King Fahd Stadium, its proximity to major highway interchanges makes it very easy for taxis and ride-hailing vehicles to navigate to and from the stadium gates.
      </p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;">Radisson Blu Hotel, Riyadh Qurtuba</h3>
      <p>
        Designed with a fresh, contemporary aesthetic, the Radisson Blu Hotel, Riyadh Qurtuba offers a balanced mix of stylish rooms and spacious private villas. The property features family-friendly swimming pools, multiple dining options serving global cuisine, and extensive modern meeting spaces. It is highly praised for its clean, efficient layout and friendly, attentive staff.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Logistical Advantage:</strong> Located in the Qurtuba district just an 8-minute drive north of King Fahd Stadium, it provides exceptionally quick access to the stadium gates via the northern bypass highway, bypassing Olaya traffic completely.
      </p>

      <h2 id="budget-apartments" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">6. Budget-Friendly &amp; Serviced Apartments</h2>
      <p>
        For families, group bookings, or fans visiting for extended stays, serviced apartments are a highly practical option. They offer significantly more living space, multiple bedrooms, and private cooking facilities, allowing you to manage your budget effectively.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Rosewood Residences Olaya</strong> (and similar premium serviced complexes) provide a home-away-from-home experience. These residences feature fully equipped kitchenettes, spacious living rooms, in-room laundry machines, and 24-hour reception services.
      </p>
      <p>
        Choosing serviced apartments in the neighborhoods surrounding the Olaya corridor puts you in close proximity to grocery stores, local bakeries, and transport links, making them the most comfortable option for long-term stays during the multi-week tournament.
      </p>

      <h2 id="transport-logistics" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">7. Stadium Transport Logistics</h2>
      <p>
        Navigating the final stretch to King Fahd International Stadium requires planning, as traffic controls will be strict on match days. Consider these transport options from your hotel:
      </p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">
          <strong>Walking (Not Recommended):</strong> Despite the relative closeness of some properties, walking to the stadium is highly discouraged. The capital’s high daytime temperatures and the massive multi-lane highway corridors surrounding the stadium grounds make pedestrian travel unsafe and uncomfortable.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">
          <strong>Riyadh Metro (Red Line):</strong> Taking the automated Metro Line 2 (Red Line) to the closest designated stadium transit station is the most efficient travel option. This route completely bypasses highway traffic, delivering you directly to the pedestrian ticket gates in air-conditioned comfort.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">
          <strong>Ride-Hailing (Uber/Careem):</strong> Taxis and ride-hailing services are highly reliable in Riyadh. A typical ride from the Olaya hotel cluster to the stadium gates costs between 15 and 25 SAR ($4.00 – $6.60 USD) and takes approximately 5 to 10 minutes under normal traffic conditions. On match days, make sure to leave early to account for road closures and security checkpoints.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="faqs" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--gold); margin-top: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">8. Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 1.5rem;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <h4 style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: How far is King Fahd Stadium from the Olaya District?</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--white-dim);">It is approximately 5 to 10 minutes by car or direct metro connection under normal traffic conditions. This close proximity makes Olaya the absolute best base for fans attending FIFA 2034 matches.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <h4 style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Do these hotels offer FIFA 2034 shuttle services?</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--white-dim);">Yes. During major international events and tournaments, most 4-star and 5-star hotels in Riyadh coordinate dedicated group shuttles for match ticket holders. It is recommended to contact your hotel directly to confirm shuttle timings closer to the tournament.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <h4 style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Can I cook my own meals in serviced apartments?</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--white-dim);">Yes. Serviced apartments (like Rosewood Residences) come equipped with kitchenettes, refrigerators, stoves, and basic cutlery, allowing families and groups to prepare their own meals easily.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </article>
  </main>
